{
  "stem": "24212.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you must have read so many times about cattle cars and what have you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we took about three days.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's all along Slovakia, and then a piece of Poland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The interesting thing about Auschwitz and the location, 'everybody' quote, unquote, knows that Auschwitz is in Poland, but the irony is that Auschwitz, at that time, was in Germany because of the movement of the borders, and because the Germans annexed Western Poland to-- to the Reich.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, the train, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, no food, no toilet facilities, barely a place to sit down, although the train had some compartments, you know, for humans, but that probably was taken up by the German police.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't go through the train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But where we were, it was pretty miserable and smelly and dark, and people screaming and crying and cursing, but mostly no food and no water.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was very shameful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Don't forget, I was a very young girl.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was ashamed to go to the bathroom in front of all kinds of people I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Other resisters, smugglers, black marketeers, you name it-- the scum.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were part of the scum.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the-- the arrival at Auschwitz was like a phantasmagorical picture that you read in-- I don't know. is a fairy tale, compared with it, though.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was dark.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was night.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Or it was too early in the morning, so that it was dark.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you saw the fires going out of the chimneys.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Not smoke-- you didn't see the smoke because of that, but you saw the fire.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
